---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 119
By: Sri Chandrasekhara Bhârati Swâmigal
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Sacrifice and Suffering=Suffering Inseparable From the
    Fallen State
---
If we want to be without any sort of pain, we must ascertain first the cause
of pain. A little consideration will make it clear to us that the root cause
of all sorrow is the mistaken identification of the Self with the body. ...
Ignorance alone is the prime cause of all misery.
